{"id": "hardware-development--zindello-industries-ultrapeater-1w-pymc-repeater", "title": "Zindello Industries Ultrapeater - 1W pyMC repeater", "forum": "hardware-development", "messages": [{"id": "1494079990159904838", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, April 15, 2026 5:00 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-15 5:00 p.m.", "text": "I've been working on a new product. It's a LuckFox Pico Ultra based E22P 1W (30dbm) shield. The device runs pyMC and has a lot of options. pyMC allows you to: Run a MeshCore repeater LetsMesh/Meshmapper observers Custom MQTT integrations Room Server TCP companions (connect over wifi on your network) The boards are currently available with an E22 900M30S radio (covers 868/915 but an external filter is recommended in noisy environments) or an E22915M30S (Built-in filter for use in the the 915MHz band). I've wrapped it up with a software install guide, accessories, 3d printed case (or printable, the file is in the repo), along with other accessories in the store. We now have a few of these running in Aus, the UK and NZ, it would be great to see the product grow. I'd appreciate support from anyone who wants one. I have a few left in stock right now before I get the next batch done. I ship worldwide. https://zindello.com.au/ultrapeater (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;ve been working on a new product. It&#39;s a LuckFox Pico Ultra based E22P 1W (30dbm) shield. The device runs pyMC and has a lot of options. pyMC allows you to:\n<ul><li>Run a MeshCore repeater</li><li>LetsMesh/Meshmapper observers</li><li>Custom MQTT integrations</li><li>Room Server</li><li>TCP companions (connect over wifi on your network)</li></ul>\nThe boards are currently available with an E22 900M30S radio (covers 868/915 but an external filter is recommended in noisy environments) or an E22915M30S (Built-in filter for use in the the 915MHz band).\n\nI&#39;ve wrapped it up with a software install guide, accessories, 3d printed case (or printable, the file is in the repo), along with other accessories in the store.\n\nWe now have a few of these running in Aus, the UK and NZ, it would be great to see the product grow.\n\nI&#39;d appreciate support from anyone who wants one. I have a few left in stock right now before I get the next batch done.\n\nI ship worldwide.\n\n<a href=\"https://zindello.com.au/ultrapeater\">https://zindello.com.au/ultrapeater</a></span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Wednesday, April 15, 2026 6:59 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-author-container><a class=chatlog__embed-author-link href=\"https://zindello.com.au/author/josh/\"><div class=chatlog__embed-author>josh</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://zindello.com.au/ultrapeater><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">UltraPeater</div></a></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/6On1ZDqp7nguZe-pBzMQjCr-rCHYMGTf3VRk6CuA-VE/%3Ffit%3D600%252C450%26ssl%3D1/https/i0.wp.com/zindello.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5850-scaled.jpeg> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/6On1ZDqp7nguZe-pBzMQjCr-rCHYMGTf3VRk6CuA-VE/%3Ffit%3D600%252C450%26ssl%3D1/https/i0.wp.com/zindello.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5850-scaled.jpeg alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=\"https://i0.wp.com/zindello.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_5850-scaled.jpeg?fit=600%2C450&amp;ssl=1\"> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079991149887529/IMG_5895.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=9511781033cd463ed7fb529abbb64a5ff87d857bf951ddfa2d4f90783cffd1fe&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079991149887529/IMG_5895.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=9511781033cd463ed7fb529abbb64a5ff87d857bf951ddfa2d4f90783cffd1fe&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_5895.jpeg (4.07 MB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079992168976474/IMG_5889.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=a63479b54dd5bc37acb6b1d353c67ba3d3ac7b07b17741ef6b00216ec1139f85&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079992168976474/IMG_5889.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=a63479b54dd5bc37acb6b1d353c67ba3d3ac7b07b17741ef6b00216ec1139f85&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_5889.jpeg (2.38 MB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079992953573616/IMG_5898.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=74e5c8977855f332329b6e7a784c3f132e808aaaebe03894d25c7361caad0e80&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494079992953573616/IMG_5898.jpeg?ex=69ebd9ec&amp;is=69ea886c&amp;hm=74e5c8977855f332329b6e7a784c3f132e808aaaebe03894d25c7361caad0e80&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_5898.jpeg (2.4 MB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=heart><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=❤️ src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/2764.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>3</span></div><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div><div class=chatlog__reaction title=fire><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🔥 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f525.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494239900260765706", "author": "Dave", "author_handle": "dave1714", "user_id": "253384173253820416", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Thursday, April 16, 2026 3:35 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-16 3:35 a.m.", "text": "Built my ultrapeater 1W base station. 100% recommend it. 1W + py_MC = awesome. Very easy to setup with the guide and provided install scripts. Just need to install the OS, SSH in and run the provided scripts. (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Built my ultrapeater 1W base station. 100% recommend it. 1W + py_MC = awesome. Very easy to setup with the guide and provided install scripts. Just need to install the OS, SSH in and run the provided scripts.</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Thursday, April 16, 2026 3:45 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239900491583538/signal-2026-04-16-161854_004.jpeg?ex=69ebc619&amp;is=69ea7499&amp;hm=b4789f733383b6c1cfbe51174f6ce78ac3ba29119418f61865b71cd7de9ef88f&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239900491583538/signal-2026-04-16-161854_004.jpeg?ex=69ebc619&amp;is=69ea7499&amp;hm=b4789f733383b6c1cfbe51174f6ce78ac3ba29119418f61865b71cd7de9ef88f&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: signal-2026-04-16-161854_004.jpeg (545.37 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239900885844069/signal-2026-04-16-161854_003.jpeg?ex=69ebc61a&amp;is=69ea749a&amp;hm=8117f638d88d9b478f803dabc281bec9d9bb82dc33bbf5792f227bc424e9c044&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239900885844069/signal-2026-04-16-161854_003.jpeg?ex=69ebc61a&amp;is=69ea749a&amp;hm=8117f638d88d9b478f803dabc281bec9d9bb82dc33bbf5792f227bc424e9c044&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: signal-2026-04-16-161854_003.jpeg (601.79 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239901288370217/signal-2026-04-16-161854_002.jpeg?ex=69ebc61a&amp;is=69ea749a&amp;hm=66ae33961a4224de16e1afe7429705ddad844cac00c2bf356347807b4a6119b2&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1494079990159904838/1494239901288370217/signal-2026-04-16-161854_002.jpeg?ex=69ebc61a&amp;is=69ea749a&amp;hm=66ae33961a4224de16e1afe7429705ddad844cac00c2bf356347807b4a6119b2&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: signal-2026-04-16-161854_002.jpeg (492.45 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=heart><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=❤️ src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/2764.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494837473212108980", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, April 17, 2026 7:10 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-17 7:10 p.m.", "text": "Just letting everyone know that as of right now, the E22P modules are on backorder. I still have a small stock of the E22 on hand. I have more coming but it'll be a couple of weeks before more radio boards arrive.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Just letting everyone know that as of right now, the E22P modules are on backorder. I still have a small stock of the E22 on hand. I have more coming but it&#39;ll be a couple of weeks before more radio boards arrive.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494907693914259556", "author": "woketothetruth", "author_handle": "woketothetruth", "user_id": "544068302922842133", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/544068302922842133/d754f5cb0153773147e4b1cbbf43214f.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, April 17, 2026 11:49 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-17 11:49 p.m.", "text": "Have you a rough estimate as to how much it would cost to ship to the United States?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Have you a rough estimate as to how much it would cost to ship to the United States?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=zindello>zindello (VK2MES)</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1494837473212108980')\"> Just letting everyone know that as of right now, the E22P modules are on backorder. I still have a small stock of the E22 on hand. I have more coming but it&#39;ll be a couple of weeks before more radio boards arrive. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1494907962991579226", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, April 17, 2026 11:50 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-17 11:50 p.m.", "text": "You can get an exact amount via the website, IIRC it was about $22AUD plus 10% on the total order for packing/tarrifs. Unfortunately for US shipments I have to pay tarrifs and an admin fee upfront, so I have to charge those to the customer. There used to be a small item import duty exemption for items under (I think?) $100, but ... not anymore. (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>You can get an exact amount via the website, IIRC it was about $22AUD plus 10% on the total order for packing/tarrifs. Unfortunately for US shipments I have to pay tarrifs and an admin fee upfront, so I have to charge those to the customer. There used to be a small item import duty exemption for items under (I think?) $100, but ... not anymore.</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, April 18, 2026 1:33 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=ok_hand><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👌 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44c.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1495362492803711137", "author": "Dave", "author_handle": "dave1714", "user_id": "253384173253820416", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Sunday, April 19, 2026 5:56 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-19 5:56 a.m.", "text": "Been measuring power output of the device. At idle its between 0.63-0.65w with Wifi. Tx spikes get up around 4.5w. Gonna give a solar setup a go using https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005009086362285.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.5.13b81802za0bul . A diy build is cheaper but I cbf. Maths seems to check out for my area to survive winter on low-mid duty cycle loads. (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Been measuring power output of the device. At idle its between 0.63-0.65w with Wifi. Tx spikes get up around 4.5w.\n\nGonna give a solar setup a go using <a href=\"https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005009086362285.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.5.13b81802za0bul\">https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005009086362285.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.5.13b81802za0bul</a>. A diy build is cheaper but I cbf. Maths seems to check out for my area to survive winter on low-mid duty cycle loads.</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Sunday, April 19, 2026 5:56 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1495390080494469120", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, April 19, 2026 7:46 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-19 7:46 a.m.", "text": "Yea with a decent solar setup they should be ok. They’re a full Linux system so it’ll never be esp or nRF numbers.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Yea with a decent solar setup they should be ok. They’re a full Linux system so it’ll never be esp or nRF numbers.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1495404287105433640", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, April 19, 2026 8:42 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-19 8:42 a.m.", "text": "Be interesting to know what it’s like with wifi disabled", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Be interesting to know what it’s like with wifi disabled</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1495581323518279872", "author": "Dave", "author_handle": "dave1714", "user_id": "253384173253820416", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Sunday, April 19, 2026 8:26 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-19 8:26 p.m.", "text": "Thought it was pretty low overall. Seems to be lower than the pi alternatives.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Thought it was pretty low overall. Seems to be lower than the pi alternatives.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1495682340855349329", "author": "zindello (VK2MES)", "author_handle": "zindello", "user_id": "1093237236419539156", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1093237236419539156/900e5881ac93c56946ab824459391f46.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, April 20, 2026 3:07 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-04-20 3:07 a.m.", "text": "@Dodgy Andi Kirbi", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"nickvass\">@Dodgy Andi Kirbi</span></span></div>", "embeds_